select public.seed_structured_concept('expansion-batch-11','blood-spill','Safety and Infection Control','environmental blood-spill cleanup','blood spills across a treatment-room floor','Restrict the area, wear appropriate PPE, remove material safely, and use an approved disinfectant','Report splashes to eyes, mouth, nonintact skin, or sharps injuries immediately','An unprotected worker sustains mucous-membrane exposure','Clean with bare hands','Use an unapproved household product','Leave sharps hidden in towels','Safety and Infection Prevention and Control');
